      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·009.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">干旄.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>孑孑干旄，在浚之郊，素絲紕之，良馬四之，彼姝者子，何以畀之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Conspicuously rise the staffs with their ox-tails,
In the distant suburbs of Tseun,
Ornamented with the white silk bands;
There are four carriages with their good horses;
That admirable gentleman, —
What will he give them for this?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sheking-1871-ocr">
