      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·009.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">干旄.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>孑孑干旟，在浚之都，素絲組之，良馬五之，彼姝者子，何以予之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Conspicuously rise the staffs with their falcon-banners,
In the nearer suburbs of Tseun,
Ornamented with the white silk ribbons;
There are five carriages with their good horses.
That admirable gentleman, —
What will he give them for this?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
