      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·009.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">干旄.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>孑孑干旌，在浚之城，素絲祝之，良馬六之，彼姝者子，何以告之。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Conspicuously rise the staffs with their feathered streamers,
At the walls of Tseun,
Bound with the white silk cords.
There are six carriages with their good horses;
That admirable gentleman, —
What will he tell them for this?</seg>
      </tuv>
